Class Estate

java.lang.Object
Owner
Estate
Direct Known Subclasses:
ResidentialEstate
public class Estate extends Owner
Represents a real estate property with details such as name, location, price, and ownership. Inherits owner information from the Owner class.

Each Estate object contains:

  • Name of the estate
  • Location of the estate
  • Price of the estate
  • Owner's name and phone number (inherited)
